		<li>3 columns wide on large devices (&ge; 992px)</li>
		<li>4 columns wide on medium devices (&ge; 768px)</li>
		<li>6 columns wide on small devices ((&ge; 576px)</li>
		<li>12 columns (full width) on extra small devices (&lt; 576px)</li>
	</ul>
